Deathrun_silenthill_v2

Based on the movie and game of Silent Hill. 
62 CT spawns 2 terror spawns.

This map is not easy, it requires some skills. So please don't judge the map by its difficulty.

Made by: KeV
Thanks to: Fibbs
Tested by: Metz, Pinhead, Maffe, York-York, Yorkie & Zippo
Cannon prefab by: $ol!d$sn4ke and go0b3rxFTW
Fan prefab by: Fibbs

v1 Notes:

- Bunnyhop made easier (change delayed by 0.5 seconds)
- Fixed badly textured door (thanks Metz ^^)
- Removed exploitable board of wood
- Easier access to secret area

v2 notes:

- Fixed leak (Fibbs ftw!)
- Texture facelift
- Replaced poor trap
- Better looking first trap
- Better lighting in some areas
- Added timer
- Other various tweaks


This will probably be my last map, so I hope you enjoy it,
KeV.
